<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="174" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1437,223,322]" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,225,223,249]" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">Notes.</emphasis>
Reported from: 
<collectingRegion box="[413,574,223,250]" country="Austria" name="Niederoesterreich" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">Lower Austria</collectingRegion>
(NÖ). 
<bibRefCitation author="Franz, H." box="[656,802,223,250]" pageId="23" pageNumber="174" refId="ref19518" refString="Franz, H. (1989) Die Nordost-Alpen im Spiegel ihrer Landtierwelt. Eine Gebietsmonographie. Umfassend Fauna, Faunengeschichte, Lebensgemeinschaften und Beeinflussung der Tierwelt durch den Menschen. Diptera, Cyclorapha. Universitatsverlag Wagner, Innsbruck, 445 pp." type="book" year="1989">Franz (1989)</bibRefCitation>
published one single record from 
<collectingCountry box="[1188,1274,223,249]" name="Austria" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">Austria</collectingCountry>
. We think it is very likely that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schummel" authorityYear="1842" box="[328,408,259,286]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Callicera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="174" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufa">
<emphasis box="[328,347,260,286]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[361,408,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">rufa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in 
<collectingCountry box="[522,608,259,285]" name="Austria" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">Austria</collectingCountry>
. However, due to confusion with other species within the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Panzer 1809" authorityName="Panzer" authorityYear="1809" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Callicera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="174" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1330,1436,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">Callicera</emphasis>
Panzer 
<quantity box="[234,290,295,321]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.59486" pageId="23" pageNumber="174" unit="in" value="1809.0">1809</quantity>
</taxonomicName>
in the past, it is necessary to re-examine voucher specimens before 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schummel" authorityYear="1842" box="[1052,1131,295,322]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Callicera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="174" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufa">
<emphasis box="[1052,1071,296,322]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1084,1131,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="174">rufa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be included in the list.
</paragraph>
